分析¶

DSSD$A'_i$$E_i =kA_i+b $$(k,b)$$x_{im}$ $k_{x_{im}},b_{x_{im}}$x$m_x$, y$m_y$, xy $$ \begin{align} E_x=k\sum_\limits {i}A_{xi}+m_xb \\ E_y=k\sum_\limits {j}A_{yj}+m_yb \end{align} $$ $E_x=E_y$, $$ \text{x1es-y1es} = \sum_\limits {i}A_{xi}-\sum_\limits {j}A_{yj}=(m_y-m_x)\frac{b}{k} \tag{1} $$

  • $m_x=m_y$0

  • b

    • DSSD1A' $b/k\approx$ -25.

对幅度A'进行修正¶

  • $A''$
$$ \begin{align} A''_i &= A'_i+b/k \tag{2}\\ E_i &=kA_i+b = k(A''_i-b/k)+b\\ \to E_i &= kA''_i \tag{3} \end{align} $$

$$ \text{x1es'-y1es'} = \sum_\limits {i}A'_{xi}-\sum_\limits {j}A'_{yj}=0 \tag{4} $$

(a) DSSD 15 16 :AB C D (Pedestal) (b) (a) 16 15 ( 100 ch)

  • $40/6000=0.006$,
